Invocation Name: random fast food
des:
If you start the skill, you will get a random suggesting restaurant.
The random generator will choose between following restaurants:
1. MC Donald´s
2. Kentucky Fried Chicken
3. Subway
5. Burger King
6. Doner of your trust
7. Dunkin Donuts

Are you missing a restaurant? Let me know it in the review!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
